description:
Rarely available oceanfront vacation rental at the famous Kahala Beach Apartments. Now is the time to enjoy this iconic beachfront location, don't wait to experience island living like no other on Oahu. New law requires a 90-day booking to stay at this unit but 3-months will go by so quickly when you're waking up to the Pacific Ocean outside your bedroom window every morning. 90-days will give you enough time to truly settle into an island lifestyle routine, learn more about the neighborhood, the culture and customs of what it means to live in Hawaii. This grand unit features 3, 450 sq. ft. of living space with 3-bedrooms & 3.5 bathrooms. You and your guests will have ample room to call home and be able to unwind and relax with enough space to keep all guests happy. 6+ month option available at $15, 000/month + GE tax.
Enjoy beach and ocean access from the Kahala Beach Apartments, as well as on-site amenities: a heated swimming pool and exercise room. Stroll next door to The Kahala Hotel & Resort for shopping, dining and live music at The Veranda.

description:
At the blue Pacific Ocean's edge and elevated one story above the sand at Kaimana Beach, this spacious studio could be your pied-à-terre home away from home. Sans Souci epitomizes its definition, “without worry”, as one of many secure residential buildings defining Honolulu's Gold Coast — to Hawaiians past, kapua, “the flower”. Swaying palms will inspire you by day as waves lull you to peaceful sleep each night. Choose to sleep on its lanai, large enough to function as a bedroom and furnished with a comfy wall bed, or opt for the interior sofa sleeper. Sans Souci offers you unparalleled access to healthy living - swim, snorkel, dive, kayak, hike, bike, yoga, lots of eateries from casual to fine dining like the Hau Tree restaurant and Michels restaurant; short distances to shopping galore; personal services and medical care; groceries and farmer's markets; Outrigger Canoe Club and Elk's Lodge are next door.
